rows.text: Old Portuguese Churches, tower and caves
Portuguese Monastery over the cave & the large watch tower on the adjoining hill

Covered colonnade (to the south of the well)

Old Temple & Viragals or sculptural memorial stones
Temple of Haranareshwar & Ardhanarinateshwar, one Hemadpanthi tank (small square kunda) & Vinagal stone kept in the comound.
Tank by the west side of ther road from Umarale village to Bolinj
